original_title: Spider-Man XXX 2: An Axel Braun Parody
overview: Everybody's favorite wallcrawler joins forces with power woman to neutralize an aim splinter cell in Sin City, when they cross paths with a new villain, Mysterio! Luckily, Arachne comes to the rescue... In more ways than one.
